How-To-Repeat: 
$ echo -en  "\tGGG\nJJJ\nccc"
-en \tGGG\nJJJ\nccc
$ 

but:

$ echo -e  "\tGGG\nJJJ\nccc"
        GGG
JJJ
ccc
$

